text: Franco Chino (born 27 September 1948) is a retired Italian backstroke swimmer. He competed in the 100 m and 200 m events at the 1968 Summer Olympics, but failed to reach the finals. ==References== Category:1948 births Category:Living people Category:Male backstroke swimmers Category:Swimmers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Italian male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Italy
